---
layout: layouts/base.njk
permalink: /blog/
title: From the Den
metaTitle: From the Den — BuilderFox Dev Blog
description: "The BuilderFox dev blog: design deep-dives, roster reveals, and milestone updates from Wrestling City Tactics. Posted when it's real, not on a schedule."
schema: blog
---
    <section class="section blog-index grid-bg" aria-labelledby="blog-title">
      <div class="container">
        <header class="page-header reveal">
          <p class="eyebrow">// BuilderFox dev blog</p>
          <h1 id="blog-title">From the Den</h1>
          <p class="lead">Major updates from BuilderFox &mdash; design deep-dives, roster reveals, and honest milestone reports from Wrestling City Tactics.</p>
        </header>
        <ol class="post-list reveal" reversed>
          {%- for post in collections.post | reverse %}
          <li class="post-card">
            <p class="post-date"><time datetime="{{ post.date | isoDate }}">{{ post.date | readableDate }}</time></p>
            <h2 class="post-card-title"><a href="{{ post.url }}">{{ post.data.title }}</a></h2>
            <p class="post-card-desc">{{ post.data.description }}</p>
          </li>
          {%- endfor %}
        </ol>
        <p class="list-note">That&rsquo;s everything so far. We post on milestones, not a schedule.</p>
      </div>
    </section>
